{"tid":1234933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"做緊海外文宣嘅朋友,想研究吓點對付呢啲youtuber","createTime":"2019-06-17T04:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T08:09:02.000Z","uid":42675,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"22af20f531d5d653b2de2adeaa10b4a6d534509c","tid":1234933,"uid":42675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:36:28.000Z","msg":"TLDR:<br />\n唔該走上去比個dislike<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PCokRDKR89c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPCokRDKR89c&d=4IeBTxJtadAFWj01jWWaWqb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=eac9aabb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PCokRDKR89c</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kRwPJkQEEPQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkRwPJkQEEPQ&d=4IeBTxJtadAFWj01jWWaWqb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=33514fa1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kRwPJkQEEPQ</a><br />\n<br />\n我記得前幾個post見過有巴打話<br />\n如果比中共喺貿易戰回到氣<br />\n就會比佢有餘力用英文喺海外打大量文宣戰<br />\n但呢種事情其實已經係發生緊<br />\n呢啲youtuber用片面嘅資料扮中立同深入分析香港嘅情況<br />\n將是非黑白顛倒,稱香港人冇理解到修例內容而係比人煽動<br />\n不幸嘅係呢啲youtuber觀看次數一啲都唔少<br />\n甚至係Hong Kong Protests / extradition呢個keyword下最多人睇嘅片之一<br />\n外國人同海外華人對香港逃犯條例唔會太熟<br />\n當佢地上youtube search頭幾條片就係呢種懶係解釋嘅影片時<br />\n個負面影響都咪話唔細<br />\n<br />\n小弟英文唔算好叻,使用法律字眼更加係唔夠水平<br />\n出唔到一條片去解釋點解要阻止修例<br />\n只能喺留言同佢地簡單講返反對嘅理由<br />\n當然,喺呢啲片底下咁嘅留言係唔會存活到幾耐<br />\n所以依家仲研究緊對抗呢種youtuber嘅方法<br />\n但在此之前,希望各位巴打走上去比個dislike<br />\n佢地刪得到留言刪唔走負評,都對件事都會有幫助<br />\n<br />\n香港加油,Proud of Hong Kong<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a12d5bf015f356ea51b8620b9e4b9ae53ac76862","tid":1234933,"uid":42675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:40:03.000Z","msg":"自推,忙緊其他野嘅巴打<br />\n上去比個dislike都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f5e44fbd5677e75d4cf07ad1856c8d1541f044","tid":1234933,"uid":42675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:53:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dde98f7ce7b1